{"tid":2288104,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"蓬佩奧的「一中三表」 （長平）","createTime":"2020-11-16T09:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T08:40:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"63f437ec36d2344fb5c1b29ab84fa15972452a6a","tid":2288104,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201116/YYCSZBMANBHYPARIDOHHIHXIKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201116%2FYYCSZBMANBHYPARIDOHHIHXIKU%2F&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=dc70e8a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201116%2FYYCSZBMANBHYPARIDOHHIHXIKU%2F&h=409f8fbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201116/YYCSZBMANBHYPARIDOHHIHXIKU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧的「一中三表」 （長平）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9ooQWJG0r69ejkzIVmruEg_0oH8=/1284x700/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K2MW33ZE35GKLD6MBEXVD6IY2M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9ooQWJG0r69ejkzIVmruEg_0oH8%3D%2F1284x700%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK2MW33ZE35GKLD6MBEXVD6IY2M.gif&h=0735b171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「台灣一直不是中國的一部份」，美國國務卿蓬佩奧11月12日接受媒體採訪時說。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧並非隨便一說，而是認為「措辭正確總是很重要」。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n聽上去有些耳熟？沒錯，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中國早就意識到這個文字遊戲的危險，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從「人類公敵」到「人渣」<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人汪文斌。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧的第三「表」讓中共震怒。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n新華網發表評論說：在涉及中國的問題上，蓬佩奧「幾乎沒說過正確的話」，「每。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n北京為甚麼如此震怒？從表面上看，是因為。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在美國大選之前，已經有專家表示擔心，認為北京會趁華盛頓手忙腳亂之時突襲台灣。果然，特朗普不承認敗選，他對選票公正性的質疑帶來了混亂。但是，顯然，中共並沒有攻打台灣的準備。<br />\n<br />\n前美國情報官保羅希爾（Paul Heer）說過，中國並不是在找攻打台灣的機會。恰恰相反，它一直在找不攻打台灣的借口。北京對民進黨的憤怒，主要不是因為它要搞「台獨」，而是這樣做等於是在激將它動手。天可憐見，北京多年來所言所行其實就是「千萬別逼我動手，因為我實在沒有辦法動手啊」。由此可以想見，蓬佩奧的火上加油讓北京多麼惱火。<br />\n<br />\n這種時候，話語一定要最強硬：「中華民族早已經不是東亞病夫，中華大地早已不是外國勢力可以胡來的競技場。&hellip;&hellip;想插手中國內政，圖謀分裂中國，只會撞得頭破血流。」<br />\n<br />\n長平<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員"},{"pid":"0395f6f1cc3d355b3510c6c6a8b70fa43a3299a4","tid":2288104,"uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:59:05.000Z","msg":"「千萬別逼我動手，因為我實在沒有辦法動手啊」"},{"pid":"37185e71b9f4b064a86f49eadab809852bb88df6","tid":2288104,"uid":271130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"你唔好迫我出手打你呀屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔撚夠打呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db3544c404a41466c06a62de4aa8c3c6e956b45","tid":2288104,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:11:33.000Z","msg":"台獨呢個話題唔存在"},{"pid":"4f9c9f89ff2647139788cc26d422268f3e69b510","tid":2288104,"uid":38962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:15:35.000Z","msg":"我出手連我自己都驚"},{"pid":"9ae195fbada8640dcb9da4b7c5751df8d0365867","tid":2288104,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0395f6f1cc3d355b3510c6c6a8b70fa43a3299a4","tid":2288104,"uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:59:05.000Z","msg":"「千萬別逼我動手，因為我實在沒有辦法動手啊」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:18:00.000Z","msg":"由此可以想見，蓬佩奧的火上加油讓北京多麼惱火。"},{"pid":"d2a07bb872abd0f709f6cd5a9c9cb352ee445dd9","tid":2288104,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:21:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">一早屌左毒果係僭維撚党報&quot;，尤其小心呢隻專職雜種打狗&quot;長平&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\